  "prompt": "How do I get call history for my Airtel prepaid number?",
  "response": "Getting the call history for your Airtel prepaid number can be accomplished through several methods. Here\u2019s how you can do it:\n\n1. **Via USSD Code:**\n   Airtel does not generally offer call history via USSD codes due to privacy and security reasons. However, you can use USSD codes for balance inquiries and other services.\n\n2. **Through Airtel Thanks App:**\n   - Download the Airtel Thanks app from the Google Play Store or Apple App Store if you don't already have it.\n   - Open the app and log in with your Airtel number.\n   - Navigate to the \u2018Usage\u2019 or \u2018Account Details\u2019 section, where you may find details about your recent calls, SMS, and data usage.\n\n3. **Online Customer Portal:**\n   - Visit the Airtel official website.\n   - Log in with your mobile number and OTP.\n   - Navigate to the \u2018My Account\u2019 section and look for call history or usage details.\n\n4. **Customer Care:**\n   - You can call Airtel customer care by dialing 121 from your Airtel number and request call history details.\n   - You might need to provide specific information for authentication purposes.\n   - Note that customer care can provide call details only for a limited period, and in some cases, you might need to visit an Airtel store.\n\n5. **Email Requests:**\n   - Send an email request to Airtel\u2019s customer service (email address could be found on their website).\n   - Provide your mobile number and any necessary identification information.\n   - Airtel might email you your call history after verifying your identity.\n\n6. **Physical Airtel Store:**\n   - Visit the nearest Airtel service center or store.\n   - Provide them with appropriate identification.\n   - Request your call history details; they may provide printouts or help you access them online.\n\nPlease note that due to privacy policies, the availability of detailed call history may be limited, and Airtel may only provide recent records. Always ensure you are following secure and official Airtel channels to request any personal information.",
